**Cooldown System**
====================

### Overview

A cooldown system is used to prevent an action from being performed too frequently. This can be useful in games, applications, or other situations where you want to limit the rate at which a certain action can be taken.

### Code

```javascript
class Cooldown {
  constructor(duration) {
    this.duration = duration;
    this.lastActivation = 0;
  }

  canActivate() {
    const now = Date.now();
    const timeSinceLastActivation = now - this.lastActivation;
    return timeSinceLastActivation >= this.duration;
  }

  activate() {
    if (this.canActivate()) {
      this.lastActivation = Date.now();
      return true;
    }
    return false;
  }
}
```

